claim.claim-text:
1. A method comprising:
creating an opening in a substrate, the opening extending from a first surface of the substrate to a second surface of the substrate, the first surface opposite the second surface;
disposing a metal slug in the opening in the substrate;
attaching an active side of a semiconductor device to the metal slug such that the entire active side of the semiconductor device abuts the metal slug;
creating a through silicon via in the semiconductor device to extend from the active side; and
plating the through silicon via with an electrically conducting material.
